org.keyboardplaying.mapper.parser

Interface TemporalParser<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of time objects this SimpleParser converts from and to
    All Superinterfaces:
    SimpleParser<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseTemporalParser, CalendarParser, DateParser

    public interface TemporalParser<T>
extends SimpleParser<T>
    Specific version of SimpleParser for temporal objects.

    Fields converted using an implementation of this interface should declare the Temporal annotation.

    Author:
    Cyrille Chopelet (http://keyboardplaying.org)
